itunes:title: Talking T-Swift
title: Talking T-Swift
description: Today we're discussing cat-loving, Grammy-winning wonder, Taylor Swift and flexing our "Swifty" fan status! We're discussing all albums from her eponymous 'Taylor Swift' to the albums 'Evermore' and 'Folklore' that made 2020 bearable. Joining us is podcast producer extroidinaire, Kaylee Moore, the ultimate Taylor Swift fan! We're going album by album and disecting the songs that got us through breakups, carried us through a pandemic, and how Taylor has evolved as a person, and how those changes are reflected in her work. Buckle up, Swifties! This episode is for you...are you ready for it?
